class.comment: Represents a method of spawning an Entity.

enumerations.name: CHUNK_GENERATION
enumerations.comment: The Entity was spawned as part of chunk generation.

enumerations.name: SPAWNER
enumerations.comment: The Entity was spawned by a spawner.

enumerations.name: STRUCTURE
enumerations.comment: The Entity was spawned as part of a structure.

enumerations.name: BREEDING
enumerations.comment: The Entity was breeded by two entities of the same type..

enumerations.name: JOCKEY
enumerations.comment: The Entity was spawned riding or is being ridden by another Entity.

enumerations.name: EVENT
enumerations.comment: The Entity was spawned because of a world event.

enumerations.name: CONVERSION
enumerations.comment: The Entity was converted from another entity.

enumerations.name: REINFORCEMENT
enumerations.comment: The Entity was spawned because another entity of its same type called for reinforcements. See the minecraft wiki for more.

enumerations.name: TRIGGERED
enumerations.comment: A trigger caused this entity to spawn.

enumerations.name: BUCKET
enumerations.comment: The Entity was spawned by a bucket containing itself being placed down.

enumerations.name: SPAWN_EGG
enumerations.comment: The Entity was created by a spawn egg.

enumerations.name: COMMAND
enumerations.comment: The Entity was spawned by a command.

enumerations.name: DISPENSER
enumerations.comment: The Entity was created by a dispenser block.

enumerations.name: PATROL
enumerations.comment: The Entity was a part of a pillager patrol.
